%----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% VMfunWorksheet.sty — Worksheet Activity Environments for Grade 7
%
% Standalone, printable worksheet activities with maximum variety:
%   worksheetHeader      Green banner with worksheet number, name/date fields
%   worksheetSkills      Compact skills summary box
%   speedDrill           Timed fluency grid with stopwatch
%   colorByAnswer        Solve problems, color by answer key
%   matchIt              Two-column matching with draw-lines space
%   mathMaze             Math maze — follow correct answers
%   errorDetective       Find and fix mistakes in shown work
%   sortCut              Cut-out cards to sort into categories
%   mathScenario         Real-world scenario with data table + questions
%   drawSolve            Problem with drawing/work space
%   inputOutput          Function machine / pattern table
%   explainIt            Math journal writing prompt
%   circleIt             Circle correct items in a set
%
% Design philosophy:
%   - Each worksheet is a standalone, printable activity page
%   - Maximum visual variety — every worksheet type looks different
%   - Fresh lime-green primary color to distinguish from other book types
%   - ALL backgrounds near-white so the book prints well in B&W
%   - Engaging, activity-based design suited for 11-12 year olds
%   - Uses \worksheetAnswer{} — one comprehensive answer per worksheet (like puzzles)
%   - Answers appear only in the "Worksheet Solutions" chapter at the end of the book
%----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
\ProvidesPackage{VMfunWorksheet}[2026/03/02 Grade 7 Worksheet Activity Environments]

